Package: APackOfTheClones
Type: Package
Title: Visualization Of T-cell Clonal Expansion
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Qile Yang
Authors@R: c(person("Qile", "Yang", email = "qile0317@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut","cph")))
Maintainer: Qile Yang <qile0317@gmail.com>
Description: Visualize T-cell clonal expansion via cirlce-packing.
  APackOfTheClones can integrate single-cell RNA sequencing (scRNAseq) and T-cell receptor (TCR) libraries from the 10X genomics Single Cell Immune Profiling and Cell Ranger pipeline, to produce a simple, publication-ready visualization of the clonal expansion. 
  The method was originally implemented by Murray Christian and Ben Murrell in the following immunology study:
  * Ma et al. (2021) <doi:10.1126/sciimmunol.abg6356>
